            "title": "內地A股早市受壓 深指半日挫1.96% 航空股則逆市揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國首季經濟數據勝預期，卻未能扭轉A股今早下跌的走勢；生物製藥股受壓，相反航空股則在上月營運數字支持下造好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113950_source-web_00753國航-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國航官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113950_source-web_00753國航-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：國航官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早平開，見3267點即成半日高位，早市初至中段持續反覆向下，接近上午11時前才於低位略為喘定，尾市沽壓再增；滬指收接近半日低位收市，報3237點，跌30點或0.92%，半日成交2877.18億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指明顯跑輸，半日高位9814點時也跌43點，低位9663點，挫194點；深指中午收報9664點，跌193點或1.96%，成交3899.59億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌35點或0.93%，收報3726點；創業板指數跌47點或2.47%，報1882點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生物製藥板塊資金流出情況較明顯，榮昌生物(09995)A股(688331.SH)跌5.64%，報45.04元；昭衍新藥(06127)A股(603127.SH)也跌5.07%，報15.35元；昊海生科(06826)A股(688366.SH)、百濟神州(06160)A股(688235.SH)、諾誠健華(09969)A股(688428.SH)等均跌逾4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">航空股相繼公布3月份營運數字，相關股份今早齊逆市揚升。國航(00753)A股(601111.SH)漲3.06%，報7.41元；南方航空(01055)A股(600029.SH)升1.58%，報5.8元；東方航空(00670)A股(500115.SH)也升1.61%，報3.79元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14858576-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%8c%ab1-96-%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e8%82%a1%e5%89%87%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e6%8f%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-2.jpg.webp",
